{
  "stem": "19895.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were talking nonsense in the high fever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Horrible scenes of-- of-- of-- confused people from delusions from high fever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One of them was running out naked in front of the barrack because his wedding taxi arrives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I recall that scene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and I remember the day when I found that I myself have lice on my clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And under the foldings of your little coat, they were like avenues of lice, walking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then you found it in your hair, and in your pubic area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and-- and we were lice-infected.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And more and more people had typhoid fever and died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and the work, the forced labor work was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were then out in wintertime, in snow, in ice, with minimal footwear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Soaked, frozen, wet shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Frozen ice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "People were dying of typhoid fever, from malnutrition, people were-- out on the work were shot at because they didn't work fast enough.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a total terror.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Total terror how we were living from one day to the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then people started to have frozen extremities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Hands, mostly legs, which were getting no circulation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and-- and were infected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was few Jewish doctors who were among the deportees in that place, from the paramilitary units of-- coming from the Russian front, or some of those who were with our Budapest Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "These doctors were trying to deliver medical help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I, myself, were-- was getting weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This friend of mine, whom I found in Harka again, and we were sticking together, this Tomas Stern, whose name I mentioned earlier, he was getting weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We never seen a mirror, but looking at each other, we could tell that we are less and less of a human being any more.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
